{"categories":["newsletter","news-blog-and-magazines","sports","automotive"],"collections":"","description":"Immerse yourself in the high-octane world of automotive sports with this fresh, dynamic email template. Perfect for newsletters, news updates, and blog posts, it features a sleek, one-column design that's easy on the eyes, making it ideal for sharing articles or the latest news about motorcycle racing. Its light background provides a striking contrast to the vibrant red accents, mirroring the exhilarating rush of speed on the racetrack. Whether you're informing readers about the latest automotive trends, sharing thrilling racing updates, or highlighting sports magazine features, this template is your key to engaging your audience. Its clean, white space design ensures your content takes pole position every time.","short_description":"Experience the thrill of the racetrack with our dynamic email design, perfect for newsletters, blog posts and news updates in the automotive and sports industries. With a bold red and white, one-column layout, stay informed on the latest in motorcycles and racing. Ideal for racing enthusiasts and automotive bloggers.","designer":{"avatar_url":"https://d1oco4z2z1fhwp.cloudfront.net/designers/Beefree_TemplateCatalog_ProfileImage_400x400_1.png","description":"A team of passionate designers, marketers, and technologists with an understanding that great design inspires action. At Beefree, we’re committed to creating responsive, mobile-friendly, and high-converting templates that empower teams to get more done with less time.","short_description":"","display_name":"Beefree Team","id":"beefree-team"},"html_data":"<!DOCTYPE html><html xmlns:v=\"urn:schemas-microsoft-com:vml\" xmlns:o=\"urn:schemas-microsoft-com:office:office\" lang=\"en\"><head><title></title><meta http-equiv=\"Content-Type\" content=\"text/html; charset=utf-8\"><meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width,initial-scale=1\"><!--[if mso]><xml><o:OfficeDocumentSett